data.description: This beautiful contemporary home is very well kept with a open floor plan that flows. Main level is the kitchen/dining room/living room and bathroom.  3 beds upstairs along with laundry and 2 bathrooms. Lower level has a large bonus room and the garage. Backs to green space and looks out to trees. Both are protected. Great location that is close to shopping and restaurants. Garage is being used as a game room, pool table can be included in purchase along with most of the furniture can be negotiated. All appliances included. Occupied home. Appointment only.
